This repo includes docs and examples for Hojoki's API. The API enables you to plug in your favourite apps into Hojoki's newsfeed of our existing 15+ integrations including Dropbox, Github, Google Docs and Evernote. Visit http://hojoki.com for more info on Hojoki.

The API is work in progress and in private alpha up to now. To get an invite (and your API key) please contact adam@hojoki.com. He is also very happy to hear any feedback you have!